column14: One most important thing you want to improve as soon as possible
Get rid of useless meetings - daily meetings are too long and demotivating, retro meetings as well. I hope, this workshop isn't one of them)
Improve estimations (smaller stories, team vs. silo estimation)
produce more product value per time unit at given costs
I feel that we seldom work as a team, but more as two separate groups of BE and FE devs and testers, and that I would like to see changing in the upcoming PI
Long-term Product vision has to be communicated clearly
